             * 3d          | RETURNDATASIZE | 0 0 t 0 0           | [0..t): extra calldata          |
             * 35          | CALLDATALOAD   | i t 0 0             | [0..t): extra calldata          |
             * 5a          | GAS            | g i t 0 0           | [0..t): extra calldata          |
             * f4          | DELEGATECALL   | succ                | [0..t): extra calldata          |
